pl.wiraszka.ZwirekSpaceInvaders

Interface Commons

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Alien, Model, Player, Shot, View, VisualBattlefield

    public interface Commons

    Commons in Zwirek Space Invaders

    Interface that holds all constants for whole program. These constants defines many different aspects of program way of working and their change can affect how program works. Is implemented by most of program classes.
    Author:
    Maciej Wiraszka
